long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This DevTools extension adds another panel that shows decoded FastRPC (protocol v1, v2, v3) requests and responses. The FastRPC protocol is described here: https://github.com/seznam/fastrpc/wiki/FastRPC-binary-protocol-specification
